title: Rose Blossom Punch Discography 1997-1999 (2 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
ROSE BLOSSOM PUNCH DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 2 releases...

 * 1997 - Ephemere
 * 1999 - Sorry To Disappoint You

Rose Blossom Punch is a post-grunge/alternative rock band from Seattle, Washington. It was formed in 1995 by Aaron Sprinkle and Paul Mumaw, with Poor Old Lu bassist Nick Barber and guitarist Terry Coggins.

Be Blessed,
